{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"bg_adv_23071.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":240201,"motion":1,"pos":2,"soulGem":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":200901,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"item":[{"anchor":"skip","path":"resource/scenario/img/scene0/calender_day14.png","posX":-4,"posY":-50,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"messageFront"}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"bgm":"bgm02_anime06","chara":[{"id":240201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-1"}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvColor":"textSayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Um...thanks for lending me that movie.","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":200901,"motion":400,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-2"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Oh, you already watched it?"},{"chara":[{"id":240201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-3"}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvColor":"textSayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Yeah. I've been wanting to watch it@for a while."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":200901,"motion":1,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-4"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]So...what did you think of it?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":240201,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-5"}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvColor":"textSayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Well, I...don't think I liked this movie@that much."},{"chara":[{"id":240201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-6"}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]If you can't find happiness even when@you have talent and put in the effort..."},{"chara":[{"id":240201,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-7"}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]...it's really tragic."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":240201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-8"}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]The bad guys get punished,@and the good guy's efforts pay off."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":240201,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-9"}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]I think we need those kinds of stories, too."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200901,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-10"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]...Miss Miki."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":240201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-11"}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvColor":"textSayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Oh... Sorry.@Maybe that sounded a bit..."},{"chara":[{"id":200901,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-12"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]There's something worrying you,@isn't there?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":240201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-13"}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvColor":"textSayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Huh...?"},{"chara":[{"id":200901,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-14"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Isn't there something in your life..."},{"chara":[{"id":200901,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-15"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]...where you want someone's efforts@to pay off?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":240201,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-16"}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvColor":"textSayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Uh, um..."},{"chara":[{"id":240201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-17"}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]You're oddly perceptive at times,@Mabayu-senpai."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":200901,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-18"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Well, my mom used to be a fortune teller...@before she died."},{"chara":[{"id":200901,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-19"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]So, I have the power to see the future too.@Very faintly..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":240201,"motion":400,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-20"}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvColor":"textSayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]What...?@Wait, are you being serious?"},{"chara":[{"id":200901,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-21"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Seriously serious."},{"autoTurnFirst":3.6,"autoTurnNoDelay":1,"chara":[{"id":200901,"motion":300,"voiceFull":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-22"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]I can even divine your future,@if you'd like..."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":200901}]},{"chara":[{"id":240201,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-23"},{"id":200901,"voiceFullStop":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-22"}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvColor":"textSayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]......"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":240201,"lipSynch":1,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-24"},{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":200901,"motion":0}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Well, um...I..."},{"chara":[{"id":240201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-25"}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]I'm not really the type to believe in@fortunes and whatnot."},{"chara":[{"id":200901,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-26"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Fortune telling is pretty non-committal,@you know."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":240201,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-27"}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvColor":"textSayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Huh?"},{"chara":[{"id":200901,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-28"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Fortunes could be right or wrong."},{"chara":[{"id":200901,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-29"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]You don't need to believe in them at all."},{"chara":[{"id":200901,"motion":1,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-30"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]But if there's something you can't share@with friends, because they're too close..."},{"chara":[{"id":200901,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-31"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]A fortune teller is a stranger, so you might@be able to confide in them more honestly."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":200901,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-32"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]And by talking about it, you might be@able to resolve what's on your mind,@or organize your thoughts."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200901,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-33"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]It can have that kind of effect, sometimes."},{"bgmFadeOut":3000,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":240201,"lipSynch":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-34"}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvColor":"textSayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]......"},{"chara":[{"id":240201,"lipSynch":1,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-35"},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":200901,"motion":0}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Well, I..."},{"bgm":"bgm02_anime02","chara":[{"id":240201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-36"}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]I have this childhood friend."},{"chara":[{"id":240201,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-37"}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]He's been good at playing the violin@ever since he was little. A real genius."},{"chara":[{"id":240201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-38"}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]It's thanks to him that I started@listening to classical music."},{"chara":[{"id":240201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-39"},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200901}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]But he got badly injured in an accident."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_031.exp3.json","id":240201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-40"}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]They said that he might not ever be able@to move his fingers like he used to."},{"chara":[{"id":200901,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-41"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]That's...quite tragic."},{"chara":[{"id":240201,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-42"}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvColor":"textSayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Yeah.@But what's really tough to see..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"id":240201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-43"}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]...is how he's lost his will to live.@He's like a totally different person."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":200901,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-44"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]That's...rough."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":240201,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-45"},{"eyeClose":0,"id":200901,"motion":0}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvColor":"textSayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Now, this is just a what-if, but..."},{"chara":[{"id":240201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-46"}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Imagine that there's a really expensive@surgery available overseas that could@restore the use of his hands."},{"chara":[{"id":240201,"motion":201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-47"}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]And imagine that I had the means@to pay for it all..."},{"chara":[{"id":240201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-48"}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Shouldn't I go ahead and do that for him?"},{"chara":[{"id":200901,"lipSynch":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-49"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]......"},{"chara":[{"id":200901,"lipSynch":1,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-50"},{"id":240201,"motion":0}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]That's a difficult question."},{"chara":[{"id":200901,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-51"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]An act like that would probably change@your dynamic with him dramatically."},{"chara":[{"id":200901,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-52"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]But that may not necessarily be@a good thing."},{"chara":[{"id":240201,"lipSynch":0,"motion":300}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvColor":"textSayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]......[wait:0.8][chara:240201:eyeClose_1:lipSynch_1][chara:240201:voiceFull_fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-53]Right."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":200901,"motion":1,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-54"},{"eyeClose":0,"id":240201,"motion":0,"voiceFullStop":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-53"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]I also think..."},{"chara":[{"id":200901,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-55"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]What if in that movie,@Mozart ended up deaf?"},{"chara":[{"id":200901,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-56"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Maybe it would be more like@being released from a curse."},{"chara":[{"id":200901,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-57"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]He actually might have lived@a pretty happy life, despite it all."},{"chara":[{"id":240201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-58"}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvColor":"textSayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]What...?"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":200901,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-59"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]He's been focused on the violin since he@was little, and he feels like it's all he has."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":200901,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-60"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]I can completely understand why your@friend might think that way. But..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200901,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-61"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Is that really a life that leads to happiness?"},{"chara":[{"id":200901,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-62"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]If becoming unable to play the violin@has caused him to despair..."},{"chara":[{"id":200901,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-63"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]...and he's lashing out against the@people around him because of that..."},{"chara":[{"id":200901,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-64"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Maybe what he needs isn't functioning@fingers..."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":200901,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-65"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]...but the courage to keep living@without the violin."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":200901,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-66"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Don't you think?"},{"chara":[{"id":240201,"lipSynch":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-67"}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvColor":"textSayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]......"},{"chara":[{"id":240201,"lipSynch":1,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-68"}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]...Is this the fortune telling@you were talking about?"},{"chara":[{"id":200901,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-69"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Ahh. Sorry."},{"chara":[{"id":200901,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-70"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]This isn't really fortune telling. It's more@something that I learned from my mom."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":240201,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-71"},{"id":200901,"motion":0}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvColor":"textSayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Still...@Sometimes, it feels like..."},{"chara":[{"id":240201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-72"}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]You can really see right through me."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":200901,"motion":400,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-73"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Wha?@N-no, there's no way I'd be able to..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":240201,"motion":201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-74"},{"id":200901,"motion":0}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvColor":"textSayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Thanks as always for the valuable advice!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":240201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908114-040-75"}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]I'll be sure to pay you back eventually!@Mentally, that is!"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}
